                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=doctorrock83",
                        "name": "doctorrock83",
                        "displayName": "julien PAULI",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Actual code is :\n{code}\npublic function setItemCountPerPage($itemCountPerPage)\n    {\n        $this->_itemCountPerPage = (integer) $itemCountPerPage;\n        if ($this->_itemCountPerPage == 0) {\n            $this->_itemCountPerPage = 1;\n        }\n        $this->_pageCount        = $this->_calculatePageCount();\n\/\/ ... ... ...\n{code}\n\nIf 0 is set, _itemCountPerPage is set to 1, so there cant be division by zero.\n\nHave you got a use case ?",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=doctorrock83",
                        "name": "doctorrock83",
                        "displayName": "julien PAULI",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2008-12-24T05:34:06.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2008-12-24T05:34:06.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/27647",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=catharsisjelly",
                        "name": "catharsisjelly",
                        "displayName": "Chris Lock",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Ah sorry my bad, we still might need to change something though.  Found out that I was passing a null value to setItemCountPerPage()  which made it throw the warnings regarding the divide by 0 error.  Might want to add code in to protect against that.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=catharsisjelly",
                        "name": "catharsisjelly",
                        "displayName": "Chris Lock",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2008-12-27T09:04:54.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2008-12-27T09:04:54.000+0000"
                },
                {
